---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
const title = "Verbling vs iTalki 2026: Which Tutoring Platform is Better? | LearnEnglish.Life";
const description = "Comparing Verbling and iTalki head-to-head. We look at tutor quality, pricing, platform features, and student results.";
---
<Base title={title} description={description}>
  <Header />
  <main id="main-content" class="bg-neutral-950 min-h-screen">
<article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
  <div class="mb-8">
    <span class="text-sm text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold">Comparison · Updated April 2026</span>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2 mb-4">Verbling vs iTalki: The Ultimate Showdown</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400">Both platforms offer 1-on-1 English lessons with native speakers. But which one is right for your goals and budget?</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
    <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 text-center">iTalki</h3>
      <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-500 text-center mb-4">9.2/10</div>
      <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm">The best choice for variety and budget-conscious learners. Massive selection of tutors.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 text-center">Verbling</h3>
      <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-500 text-center mb-4">8.5/10</div>
      <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm">The best choice for professional, certified teachers and a polished learning environment.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">Tutor Quality</h2>
  <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-6"><strong>iTalki</strong> has two types of tutors: Professional Teachers (certified) and Community Tutors (native speakers). This gives you more choice but requires more vetting. <strong>Verbling</strong> only accepts certified professional teachers, ensuring a higher baseline of quality.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">Pricing and Fees</h2>
  <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-6">iTalki is generally cheaper, with lessons starting as low as $5/hour. Verbling lessons usually start at $15/hour. iTalki uses a "credits" system or direct payment, while Verbling uses a simple checkout process.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">Platform Features</h2>
  <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-6">Verbling has a superior built-in classroom with integrated tools for sharing files and exercises. iTalki relies more on external tools like Skype or Zoom, though they have their own "iTalki Classroom" which is improving.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">The Verdict</h2>
  <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-12">Choose <strong>iTalki</strong> if you want the widest selection and the lowest prices. Choose <strong>Verbling</strong> if you want a guaranteed professional teacher and a better technical experience.</p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    <a href="/go/italki" class="block bg-emerald-600 text-white font-bold text-center px-6 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-emerald-500 transition">Try iTalki</a>
    <a href="/go/verbling" class="block bg-neutral-800 text-white font-bold text-center px-6 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-neutral-700 transition">Try Verbling</a>
  </div>
</article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>
